ext_descriptions.ext_description:
The following restrictions apply as regards the types of the positioned_item and of the reference_context:


if the reference_context is a Building, the positioned_item shall be a Building_section;

if the reference_context is a Space, the positioned_item shall be a Building_element;

if the reference_context is a Building_section, the positioned_item shall be a Building_item or a Building_level.
